{"tid":460961,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馮盈盈吹到成手口水：要盡力做實驗俾大家睇🤤","createTime":"2017-11-07T06:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T07:53:04.000Z","uid":54747,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12bbcdedd70c58ef453a9e2af41dda1b0be2deb5","tid":460961,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"性博士🤤🤤🤤<br />\n<br />\n學是學非》一向受觀眾歡迎，除了長知識外，最吸引是幾位靚女主持，尤其是港姐冠軍馮盈盈（網民叫她FYY），她每集相當生鬼又夠放得開，好像昨日（5日）那集，FYY又爆發，在節目中和劉穎鏇一齊吹飲管，女星一做這個動作，網民就份外留意，當然這一招是TVB經常用的套路，尤其綜藝遊戲節目，大家應該記得獎門人的JJ（賈曉晨），不過這次TVB用得高明，用吹飲管解釋伯努利原理，如何將可樂變成噴霧，雖然畫面好詳細交代這個理論，更製作動畫解釋，但網民似乎更欣賞FYY的真人演繹，討論區貼滿她吹飲管cap圖。"},{"pid":"44cb6985bf3b36cf60baa6342c6a9683659d8056","tid":460961,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"條口水絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339c3456d064abb2bf0bf3aaf76ad45083a304da","tid":460961,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇片/圖"},{"pid":"855467c586c089450b88bfa72f7e8ccca2bbc0b0","tid":460961,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條口水絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e981aa10fa9fc15b410f3b6da53236b93d35af","tid":460961,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"9b6c9b82dead0145a6b5ae6d2588a7855d63f7cd","tid":460961,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"完全想像到個畫面，唔洗圖片了"},{"pid":"6921a93950ee238ecc75aa02b3899c9e70247c53","tid":460961,"uid":54747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/143333_9234f44ee01c70140961f560f500249f.j